      "message": "nit: I\u0027d prefer to not add any new instances of \"api.run.run_once(api.file.ensure_directory,\" because I\u0027m pretty sure it doesn\u0027t do what you expect. If run_once has seen the first arg before, it does nothing. The other args are not taken into account for the \"once\" part.\n\nAlso, ensure_directory does nothing if the directory already exists, so it\u0027s harmless to call multiple times. This would mean you don\u0027t have to add the tmp_not_exist tests.\n\nMany instances in this CL.",
